videos.headline: California strikes first with 3-yard TD toss
videos.description: California quarterback Chase Garbers play-actions right and throws left to a wide-open Malik McMorris for a 3-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Cal's disastrous snap whacks QB in face at 1-yard line
videos.description: At the Oregon State 1-yard line, California fumbles the snap and turns it over, as the ball pounces off Chase Garbers' face mask on the exchange.

videos.headline: Garbers drops pass in RB's lap for 29-yard TD
videos.description: Chase Garbers slings a perfect ball to running back Patrick Laird on the wheel route, who trots in untouched for the 29-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Cal balloons lead with Garbers' 3rd TD
videos.description: Chase Garbers continues his stellar day with his third touchdown, Kanawai Noa  hauls the bullet in for the 24-yard score to open California's lead to 35-7.
